[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0101","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0037","title":"FreeBSD Metamail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 metamail 邮件处理工具存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的 MIME 邮件消息，在消息头中嵌入恶意命令。当用户使用 metamail 处理该恶意邮件时，漏洞被触发，导致以当前用户权限在系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，但需要用户主动触发邮件处理操作，影响范围较广。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0037"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.340","remediation":"升级 metamail 至已过滤 MIME 邮件头 shell 元字符的修补版本；若无法升级，建议直接卸载 metamail（pkg delete metamail）并改用 procmail 或 maildrop 等现代邮件处理工具替代；同时配置邮件客户端不自动调用 metamail 处理来自不可信来源的 MIME 邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0037"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0039","title":"SGI IRIX webdist.cgi 命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 的 webdist.cgi 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 distloc 参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符），即可绕过输入过滤执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需向目标 Web 服务发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可导致服务器被完全控制。CVSS 评分 7.3，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0039"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.717","remediation":"建议从 SGI 安全公告 19970501-02-PX 获取并安装对应 IRIX 版本的补丁。如无法立即打补丁，应删除或禁用 CGI 目录下的 webdist.cgi 程序，并确保 webdist 服务已停止。对于仍在使用 SGI IRIX 的系统，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统，因为 IRIX 已于 2006 年 12 月停止技术支持，不再提供安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1997-12.html","http://www.osvdb.org/235","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/374","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/333","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19299","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0039","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0039.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/webdist.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.1175"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0253","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0112","title":"IBM AIX CDE dtterm 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 4.2 系统中的 CDE 桌面环境 dtterm 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。未授权本地攻击者可通过向 dtterm 程序传递特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖函数返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有系统本地账号，影响 AIX 4.2 版本及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0112"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.680","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3 及以上版本，或安装 IBM 提供的相应 APAR 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/dt/bin/dtterm 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtterm），并限制可执行该程序的用户组，仅授权可信用户访问 CDE 环境。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/878","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/333","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83084/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0112.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0102","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0040","title":"多厂商 X Window System libXt 库本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"X Window System 的 Xt 库中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 libXt 库中 XtAppInitialize() 函数的溢出缺陷，通过精心构造的输入触发内存破坏，从而获取 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、FreeBSD、HP-UX、AIX、IRIX、SunOS、UnixWare 等多种 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于利用条件仅需本地访问，在多用户环境下威胁较大，已有公开的 xterm 利用代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0040"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级各厂商已修复的 X11 发行版：FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.5 及以上版本或 3.x，HP-UX 安装 HP 对应安全补丁，AIX 安装 IBM APAR 对应补丁，IRIX 升级至 6.5 及以上版本并安装 SGI 安全补丁，Solaris 安装 Sun 对应补丁簇。如无法升级，移除所有 setuid root 的 X11 程序（如 /usr/bin/X11/xterm）的 suid 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T08:41:11.703754812+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0103","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0038","title":"BSD xlock 缓冲区溢出本地代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 操作系统中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xlock 程序发送特制的超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的执行流程，实现以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生系统，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0038"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.473","remediation":"升级 xlock 至 xlockmore 2.5 及以上版本，或从操作系统厂商获取对应补丁（Sun 补丁 ID 10145）。在无法升级的环境中，限制不可信用户本地登录权限，移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位以阻止提权，或使用其他屏幕锁定工具替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0038"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0304","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0304.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0149","title":"SGI IRIX cgi-bin wrap 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统中的 cgi-bin wrap 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 参数中使用 `..`（点点）序列绕过路径限制，访问并列出服务器上任意目录的内容。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可导致敏感文件信息泄露，例如系统配置文件、用户数据等。攻击条件简单，仅需目标系统运行存在漏洞的 wrap CGI 程序即可实施。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0149"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.233","remediation":"建议升级至 SGI IRIX 6.3 及以上版本，或直接移除系统 cgi-bin 目录下的 wrap CGI 脚本。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器（如 Netscape FastTrack）配置中严格限制 cgi-bin 目录访问权限，并禁用路径穿越（..）与目录列表功能以作临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/247","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/373","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/290","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19298","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0149","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0149.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/UnAnnotated/CVE-1999-0149.xml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wrap.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0304.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0149","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0149.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0058","title":"PHP CGI 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"PHP 的 CGI 程序 php.cgi 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该溢出，导致内存损坏，从而获得目标服务器的 shell 访问权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 PHP，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0058"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.707","remediation":"立即升级至修复了 CGI 缓冲区溢出问题的 PHP 3.0.1 或更高版本；若无法升级，在 Apache 配置中通过 `<FilesMatch \"php\\.cgi\"> Deny from all </FilesMatch>` 禁用 php.cgi 的外部直接访问，并改用 mod_php 模块方式运行 PHP 脚本以消除 CGI 攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/712"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0149.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0105","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0042","title":"华盛顿大学 IMAP 与 POP 服务器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"华盛顿大学实现的 IMAP 和 POP 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向运行 imapd 服务的 Linux 系统发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成远程代码执行或任意文件读取。该漏洞影响使用华盛顿大学实现 IMAP/POP 协议套件的 Linux 系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0042"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.303","remediation":"升级 UW IMAP 至 4.5 及以上版本，该版本修复了 imapd 及 popd 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议禁用 IMAP/POP 服务，改用 SSH 隧道加密访问邮件，或在防火墙层面限制对 143/110 端口的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0042","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/340","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/imap.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/imap_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83099/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0466","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0466.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0280","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"微软 Internet Explorer 浏览器存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过构造特制的 .lnk 快捷方式文件或 .url 链接文件，诱使用户点击后在当前用户上下文环境中执行任意命令。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需身份认证，影响使用 Internet Explorer 的 Windows 系统。由于 IE 对 .lnk 和 .url 文件的处理缺乏充分校验，导致攻击者可在用户浏览网页时触发恶意操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0280"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.833","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本，或安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-013 对应补丁。该漏洞已在新版 IE 中修复，建议立即停止使用旧版 IE，改用 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。如因兼容性必须使用，可在安全设置中将「Internet 区域」和「受限站点区域」的安全级别设为「高」，并禁用「下载未签名的 ActiveX 控件」。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0280","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0280","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0280.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hjxm-3j2g-hph3/GHSA-hjxm-3j2g-hph3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/CrackerCat/simpread/blob/1ec36a5827997f39a7a815e20121b12f8d781497/md/Chrome%20Browser%20Exploitation,%20Part%201:%20Introduction%20to%20V8%20and%20JavaScript%20Internals%20-%20Jack%20Hacks.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0280.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0466.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0486","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0486.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0292","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Winpopup 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 Winpopup（信使服务）在处理用户名字段时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送包含超长用户名的弹出消息触发该漏洞，导致目标系统耗尽系统资源或信使服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。Microsoft 官方未发布针对此漏洞的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0292"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.240","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 以修复 Winpopup 消息处理中的缓冲区问题。如系统已不受支持，建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本，或在防火墙和本地安全策略中禁用 Messenger 服务（net stop messenger）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0292","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0292","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0292.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5hp9-m282-4fm5/GHSA-5hp9-m282-4fm5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d5e467d6-9db2-4f83-aa80-400388f5bd0e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0486.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0527","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0315","title":"Sun Solaris 2.4 /bin/fdformat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.4 系统中的 /bin/fdformat 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该命令在处理用户输入时未对缓冲区边界进行有效检查，本地攻击者可通过向 fdformat 程序提交特制的参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖进程内存空间并执行任意代码。成功利用此漏洞可使普通用户获得 root 权限，完全控制受影响的系统。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限，无法远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0315"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.140","remediation":"安装 Sun 针对此漏洞发布的安全补丁（对应 Sun Security Bulletin #138），或升级到 Solaris 2.5.1 及以上版本。如无法升级，立即执行 `chmod 0755 /bin/fdformat` 移除 fdformat 的 setuid root 权限位，阻止普通用户以 root 权限执行该程序。同时限制可访问 fdformat 的用户组，仅授权管理员使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/138","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/328","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0315.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0315","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0315.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0315.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-988q-hp2f-8wq8/GHSA-988q-hp2f-8wq8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0110.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/8cadbdd1cf5feac22fead0cb1d1fdbe2acdfa0e6/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-03xx/CVE-1999-0315.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0495","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0299","title":"FreeBSD lpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 的 lpd（行式打印机守护进程）在处理超长 DNS 主机名时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的打印服务发送特制的主机名数据触发该溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0299"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.117","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至已修复该漏洞的版本（4.0 及以上）。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 lpd 行并重启 inetd 以禁用打印机守护进程；若需继续使用 lpd，在 /etc/hosts.lpd 和白名单中限制允许访问的客户端 IP，并在防火墙层面阻止外部对 TCP 515 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0299","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0299.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/lpd_freebsd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83077/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0241","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0106","title":"多种厂商 Finger 服务手指炸弹漏洞","description":"Finger 服务存在重定向功能滥用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用多个支持 Finger 协议的主机构建重定向链（finger bomb），迫使目标系统反复进行网络连接，造成流量放大或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响早期运行 Finger 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。建议禁用 Finger 服务或通过防火墙限制入站访问。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0106"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.040","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（如 in.fingerd），在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释掉 finger 行并重启服务。在防火墙上阻止外部对 TCP 端口 79 的访问。如确需使用，通过 tcp_wrappers（/etc/hosts.deny）限制仅允许可信来源 IP。建议升级到支持 finger 访问控制的实现或直接停用该协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0106"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0530","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0530.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0318","title":"HP-UX XMCD 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xmcd 2.0p12 在处理环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响程序传递特制的环境变量参数触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区边界溢出并覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取目标系统的额外访问权限或提升至更高权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上运行的 xmcd 2.0p12 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级到不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0318"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.507","remediation":"升级 xmcd 至 2.1 及以上版本（该版本已修复缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法升级，可移除 xmcd 二进制文件的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xmcd`；若业务不需要 CD 播放功能，建议直接卸载 xmcd 软件包以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0318"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0530.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0892","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0612","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 Finger 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统默认安装的 finger 服务存在信息泄露漏洞。finger 协议设计上未对请求来源进行任何认证或限制，允许网络上的任何攻击者向目标主机的 finger 服务（默认端口 79）发送查询请求，从而获取系统上有效的用户名列表及其他用户账户信息。攻击者可利用收集到的有效用户名进行后续的口令猜测、暴力破解或社会工程学攻击，进一步威胁系统安全。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 等版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0612"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.177","remediation":"停止 Finger 服务（运行 services.msc，找到 \"Finger Service\" 设置为禁用），并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 79 以阻止外部访问。如需使用 finger 功能，应升级到不再内置该服务的 Windows XP 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/finger/CVE-1999-0612.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/324.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/finger.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml"}]